<refentry xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
          xmlns:svg="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:ns5="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
          xmlns:mml="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:db="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"
          xmlns:scilab="http://www.scilab.org" xml:id="zeros" xml:lang="ja">
    <refnamediv>
        <refname>zeros</refname>
        <refpurpose>ゼロからなる行列</refpurpose>
    </refnamediv>
    <refsynopsisdiv>
        <title>呼び出し手順</title>
        <synopsis>
            y = zeros(m1, m2,...)
            y = zeros(x)
            y = zeros(…, type)
            y = zeros()
        </synopsis>
    </refsynopsisdiv>
    <refsection>
        <title>引数</title>
        <variablelist>
            <varlistentry>
                <term>x, y</term>
                <listitem>
                    <para>同じサイズの配列.</para>
                </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
            <varlistentry>
                <term>m1, m2, ..</term>
                <listitem>
                    <para>整数 > 0: <varname>y</varname> のサイズ.
                    </para>
                </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
            <varlistentry>
                <term>type</term>
                <listitem>
                    <para>
                        optional character string: 'double', 'boolean','int8', 'uint8', 'int16',
                        'uint16', 'int32', 'uint32', 'int64', or 'uint64':
                        chosen <literal>typeof(y)</literal>.
                    </para>
                </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
        </variablelist>
    </refsection>
    <refsection>
        <title>説明</title>
        <para>
            ゼロ行列を作成します (<literal>0*ones</literal>と等価).
        </para>
        <variablelist>
            <varlistentry>
                <term>zeros(m1, m2,.., mn)</term>
                <listitem>
                    <para>
                        ゼロで埋めた <literal>(m1,m2,..,mn)</literal> 行列を作成します.
                    </para>
                </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
            <varlistentry>
                <term>zeros(x)</term>
                <listitem>
                    <para>
                        <varname>x</varname>の同じ大きさの行列.
                    </para>
                </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
            <varlistentry>
                <term>zeros(…, type)</term>
                <listitem>
                    <para>
                        forces the returned array to be of the given <varmane>type</varmane>. In
                        the case of boolean type, the array is filled with <literal>%F</literal> values.
                    </para>
                </listitem>
            </varlistentry>
        </variablelist>

        <para>zeros()単一のゼロを返します.</para>
        <warning>
            <literal>zeros(3)</literal>は<literal>x=3</literal>と指定した<literal>zeros(x)</literal>
            となり, すなわち, 3x3 行列とはなりません!
        </warning>
        <note>
           <literal>repmat(0, sizes)</literal> can be used to generate an array of zeros with
           <literal>sizes=[m1 m2 ..]</literal> given as a vector.
        </note>
        <para>
            <varname>x</varname> が <literal>syslin</literal> リスト
            (状態空間または伝達関数の線形システム)の場合でも,
            <literal>zeros(x)</literal> は有効で,ゼロ行列を返します.
        </para>
    </refsection>
    <refsection>
        <title>例</title>
        <programlisting role="example"><![CDATA[
zeros(3)

zeros(3,3)
z = zeros(3,3,"uint8")
typeof(z)

zeros(3,3,"boolean")

zeros(2,3,2)

m = ["a" "bc" "d" "efg" ; "h" "" "ijk" "lmn"]
zeros(m)

repmat(0, [2 4 2])
     ]]></programlisting>
        <screen><![CDATA[
--> zeros(3)
 ans  =
   0.

--> zeros(3,3)
 ans  =
   0.   0.   0.
   0.   0.   0.
   0.   0.   0.

--> z = zeros(3,3,"uint8")
 z  =
  0  0  0
  0  0  0
  0  0  0

--> typeof(z)
 ans  =
  "uint8"

--> zeros(3,3,"boolean")
 ans  =
  F F F
  F F F
  F F F


--> zeros(2,3,2)
 ans  =
(:,:,1)
   0.   0.   0.
   0.   0.   0.
(:,:,2)
   0.   0.   0.
   0.   0.   0.

--> m = ["a" "bc" "d" "efg" ; "h" "" "ijk" "lmn"]
 m  =
  "a"  "bc"  "d"    "efg"
  "h"  ""    "ijk"  "lmn"

--> zeros(m)
 ans  =
   0.   0.   0.   0.
   0.   0.   0.   0.

--> repmat(0, [2 4 2])
 ans  =
(:,:,1)
   0.   0.   0.   0.
   0.   0.   0.   0.
(:,:,2)
   0.   0.   0.   0.
   0.   0.   0.   0.
]]></screen>
